data.description: If you are looking for a large home in a great location, you definitely want to put this home on your list. This home features five bedrooms, one of which is on the first floor, with a full bath in the hallway. The master bedroom includes a walk-in closet and a master bath. There are three full bathrooms throughout the home, perfect for a large family. Space is not lacking in this home, which also consists of a large family room, living room, kitchen, and dining room. The basement is massive and can be used for additional storage or can be finished by the new owner to their liking. Call today to schedule your showing.
